<SUBJECTS>ELECTION PRESIDENTIELLE,1995,ELECTION PRIMAIRE,PARTI DE DROITE,DEPARTEMENT GERS,VIE LOCALE DES PARTIS</SUBJECTS>
<NAMES>CHIRAC JACQUES,BALLADUR EDOUARD,RISPAT YVES,MONTESQUIOU AYMERI DE,BRUSSIAU JACQUES,TOLSAU JEAN FRANCOIS,RPR,UDF</NAMES>
